DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('Customers'[SubscriptionPlan])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'Customers'[SubscriptionPlan], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'Customers'[SubscriptionPlan]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"BSNL Postpaid"}, 'Customers'[SubscriptionPlan])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'SupportTickets'[Status],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"CountIssueType", CALCULATE(COUNTA('SupportTickets'[IssueType]))
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [CountIssueType], 0, 'SupportTickets'[Status], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[CountIssueType] DESC, 'SupportTickets'[Status]

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
	TREATAS({"BSNL Postpaid"}, 'Customers'[SubscriptionPlan])

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(__DS0FilterTable, "AverageSatisfaction", IGNORE('Surveys'[AverageSatisfaction]))

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"BSNL Postpaid"}, 'Customers'[SubscriptionPlan])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'SupportTickets'[IssueType],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"AVG_ResolutionTime__hours__average_per_IssueType", 'SupportTickets'[AVG ResolutionTime (hours) average per IssueType]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			1001,
			__DS0Core,
			[AVG_ResolutionTime__hours__average_per_IssueType],
			0,
			'SupportTickets'[IssueType],
			1
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[AVG_ResolutionTime__hours__average_per_IssueType] DESC,
	'SupportTickets'[IssueType]
